               <msContents>
                  <summary>Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡, Prayer of Mary at Golgotha, ጸሎተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘሰኔ፡ ጎልጎታ፡; Sword of Divinity, ሠይፈ፡ መለኮት፡; Book of the Disciples, መጽሐፈ፡ አርድእት፡; Asmat Prayer for Strength in Travel</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="11v" facs="003">Fols 1r–11v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2444Temher">Tǝmhǝrta
                                                  ḫǝbuʾāt</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="11v" to="32r" facs="014">Fols 11v–32r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2246salotz">Ṣalot za-ʾǝgzǝʾǝtǝna
                                                  Māryām ba-Dabra Golgotā</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="32r" to="32v" facs="034">Fols 32r–32v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2295Sayfam">Sayfa malakot</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>incomplete at the end</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="33r" to="101v" facs="035">Fols 33r–101v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1915Mashaf">Maṣḥafa
                                                  ʾardǝʾt</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="103r" to="104v" facs="105">Fols 103r–104v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer for strength in travel</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ያሽሊሁ: ሸልያ: ያሸሙህሸሊያ: አጅብ: የመድ<gap reason="omitted"/> ጽሂፈ: ከመ: እስር: በ፪: አብራክ: ሶበ: ተሐውር: ኢትድክም: <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
